node.text: I’m so excited to take part in #CannesLions2021! I had an amazing conservation with @lpolgreen of @gimletmedia and @danamo to discuss music, podcasts, and the connective power of streaming audio. Enjoy this special clip and you can watch the full chat on the official Cannes Lions Live hub. Click the link in my bio ♥️
